chrome_download_cta_link.purpose: To prompt users to download or learn more about Google Chrome by navigating to its dedicated product page.
chrome_download_cta_link.reasoning: The element is an anchor tag (`<a>`) with the text 'Get Chrome', a 'cta' class (Call To Action), and an `href` attribute pointing directly to the Google Chrome download/information page. This combination clearly indicates its purpose as a primary action link for Chrome.
